sub_title: English Language Acquisition Teacher at AICS
summary:
As a Certified CELTA Trainer, I have acquired a number of skills amongst which Communicative Approach to Language and a wide range of lessons shapes and techniques. Recognized for an open mindset for new work approaches, problem-solving skills, creative thinking, and drive for results. Resourceful and well-organized with excellent management abilities. Dedicated and hardworking with an internal drive to deliver excellence.

Communicative approach
Tailor-made lessons
Creative thinking
Online teaching
Presentation skills
Assessment
Collaboration
